{"tid":2153284,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"留意到有啲冇追開刀劍神域嘅人話詩乃搶人條仔 我手上有關鍵證據證明唔係","createTime":"2020-08-12T12:17:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T08:38:04.000Z","uid":57911,"like":29,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d978751f8e7ae70811f81f6475897e23b0b68ebf","tid":2153284,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T12:17:20.000Z","msg":"現實係詩乃搶人條女<br />\n接下來我會放核彈級猛料<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家準備接招<br />\n&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ROcwbC3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FROcwbC3.jpg&h=b8bcb9ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據官方圖片顯示詩乃同亞絲娜扑過嘢<br />\n亞絲娜仲對詩乃有愛稱シノのん<br />\n詩乃登入UW世界同亞絲娜碰頭<br />\n亞絲娜含春樣飛奔過去攬實詩乃<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>由此證明，詩乃係搶人條女，唔係搶人條仔</strong></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"501d7babaa07736503c573c2028da4699938f8d5","tid":2153284,"uid":105678,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T12:18:56.000Z","msg":"很有趣的推論，刀劍神域有紅樓夢級數嘅文學價值，反刀劍就是冇文化"},{"pid":"af547336abaa771795f400175a11c73c87443532","tid":2153284,"uid":57911,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"501d7babaa07736503c573c2028da4699938f8d5","tid":2153284,"uid":105678,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T12:18:56.000Z","msg":"很有趣的推論，刀劍神域有紅樓夢級數嘅文學價值，反刀劍就是冇文化"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T12:21:19.000Z","msg":"你肯貼BC未，巴打搵得你好辛苦<br />\n<br />\n一個月已到  賤畜委員長#105678 攞到本BC出黎未?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2146197\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2146197</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5b02aa474716a55a34e9010e9e7225cee30e72cc","tid":21532